> This is a make-believe breach overview for the MyFitnessPal breach, which occurred on February 1, 2018 and was added to our database on February 21, 2019. **I am waiting for an epiphany as to how these should be localized.**

Not sure that this is epiphany worthy, but not sure if this may be as "simple" as creating a new descriptions.ftl file with the `breach.Name` as the key and the `breach.Description` as the value.

